{"tid":1226551,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"六月十六日，上街遊行，重拾身為香港人既榮耀!","createTime":"2019-06-15T12:07:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T14:48:33.000Z","uid":202464,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2ed81cc3c6b4281aa31a88a1c924ed94bd1d935e","tid":1226551,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T12:07:28.000Z","msg":"民陣反送中遊行<br />\n日期：6月16日（星期日）<br />\n遊行開始時間：2:30pm<br />\n遊行起點：維多利亞公園<br />\n遊行終點：政府總部<br />\n核心目標：撤回逃犯條例<br />\n<br />\n香港政府縱容黑警使用暴力，濫權，面對百萬市民上街遊行要求撤回送中條例，只係講句唔理解然後暫緩件事，意圖令事情淡化後重推，呢種行為我地身為香港市民係絕對不能夠接受。<br />\n<br />\n直到而家為止，黑警仍然不斷搜捕612當日有份上街遊行既市民、學生，意圖製造白色恐怖，要你地唔敢再出黎行，坐向電腦前、拎住手機既市民，縱然你沒參與呢件事，但圍觀者既沉默都會助長惡政既發生，你地係咪想將香港變成一個充滿白色恐怖既地方?<br />\n<br />\n當日出黎行既市民，我呼籲你地再出黎一次，而未出黎既市民，我都向度懇請你地出黎。呢個係屬於我地既地方，呢個係屬於我地既責任，6月16日，我地要向政府表達我地既立場，全世界睇緊我地呢壇戲，我地要將身為香港人既榮耀展示比佢地睇，鄰近既台灣已經向度恥笑我地百萬人上街咩野都做唔到，我地要同佢地講，我地唔單止可以做到，而且可以做得更好!<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人出黎啦<br />\n四大訴求，不達目的，不散!<br />\nLIVE FOR NOTHING OR DIE FOR SOMETHING<br />\n1.撤回修例<br />\n2.收回示威是暴動的定性<br />\n3.釋放所有過去一週因示威被捕的人<br />\n4.追究警方使用過份武力，甚至暴力</span></span>"},{"pid":"fc982df4b70d20690c1f553342d2091c598915d4","tid":1226551,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T12:08:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7cdaa6aa285a74cd94a84f2078c1ec0ae8bb0f8","tid":1226551,"uid":116519,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T12:08:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WFTimNR.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWFTimNR.gif&h=526c709b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f72ed84c1b13f626c59d9192d8e17972c6041b99","tid":1226551,"uid":93000,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T12:08:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"882174f4c93f101abc709f9628bbfb8357f7b34d","tid":1226551,"uid":260845,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T12:08:34.000Z","msg":"停止追究示威者責任！"},{"pid":"c78b97157bd717180f4d9396c33921b41fdb7af0","tid":1226551,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T12:08:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19059e2ed52b37ad2fe7d9c78ed5d5875f449300","tid":1226551,"uid":164313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T12:09:26.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 阻一阻你<br />\n麻煩入嚟幫推<br />\n因為「暫緩」係一個好撚難聽嘅詞語<br />\n<br />\n大家唔好以為「暫緩」係階段勝利  其實係暗地裡捉緊人 一定要盡早撤回！冇得拖！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1226062\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1226062</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0e4df13670003815386bdd4522f9471fc9e9519b","tid":1226551,"uid":202464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T12:12:50.000Z","msg":"我地今日唔會有階段性勝利<br />\n我地既目的只有幾點<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撤回修例<br />\n嚴懲黑警<br />\n釋放義士</span></span>"},{"pid":"41ac6cd3f518da89d648a389210d4467336bf5db","tid":1226551,"uid":131040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T12:13:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"66ad8540e7bd2df2243f9ed8b415c734c5e72712","tid":1226551,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T12:20:45.000Z","msg":"希望睇到既朋友，同行者，可以入黎推呢個post上熱門，我地要讓更多既市民睇到，我地需要更多既支持者<br />\n香港唔係屬於林鄭月娥一個，香港係屬於大家既!!!<br />\n我地要守護我地既民主，守護我地既正義<br />\n以往政府黑警逼我地退一步，我地就要讓一步<br />\n今日我地已經退無可退，一旦條例通過，我地將會跌入深淵<br />\n我地將唔能夠發聲，即使將來移民去第個國家，人地都只會罵你守護唔到自己既地方<br />\n我地唔應該成為二等公民，呢度係大家土生土長既地方，我地要為佢既未來負責。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">今日，你怯於政府既淫威，他日，你既仔女將會埋怨你<br />\n上一代既責任，我地呢一代黎承擔!</span></span>"},{"pid":"b1773a2564880f60d3b40a8c67bb8b74d288cc8c","tid":1226551,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T12:24:12.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"01d117b82c8763c8c1c0fe3fda7a0102fb32a233","tid":1226551,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T12:27:53.000Z","msg":"六一六，帶起你地既口罩，同我地一齊上街遊行啦!"},{"pid":"caee0d718cdc7f5a9a228027476c4c3800fc03b4","tid":1226551,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T12:28:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae891174da1f515a4d1ddcd772c5ad4798650c8d","tid":1226551,"uid":12149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T12:29:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fba5c24d96553672982258a8eb828123588cbd2","tid":1226551,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T12:35:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cf0b0f304460ccbf8224297320513837320cef3","tid":1226551,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T12:40:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1d5c91eea41c4808ff92cfc45134a45568a1f9b","tid":1226551,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T12:48:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e77cf0c49332575faaf593a226a9c809fe071872","tid":1226551,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T12:49:35.000Z","msg":"唔好比白色恐怖充斥香港"},{"pid":"aace9cf7cd475c6afdc80ebb03c80d46b13fb7e2","tid":1226551,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:05:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1332394dc059878ff9cee6416c255197904f34cc","tid":1226551,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:18:41.000Z","